VA LOAN ASSUMPTION OPTION FOR QUALIFIED BUYERS @ 2.25%!!
Location Location!! immaculately maintained home in Carolina Lakes. 1.5 story w/ pull through driveway, 2car side load garage, large front porch, screened deck overlooking the fenced backyard on golf course & less than a mile from the front gate making commute a breeze! You'll fall in love w/ this floorpan open concept great rm w/built-in bookshelves & cabinets on either side of fireplace, vaulted ceilings & wall of windows/doors w/transoms. Kitchen w/vaulted ceilings, SS appliances w/eating space in addition to a formal dining. Primary bdrm suite on main floor w/2nd bdrm & full jack-n-jill bathroom next to it. The Primary has 2 walk-in closets, double sinks, toilet closet, separate shower & jetted tub! Laundry room, another full bathrm & 2 more bedrooms on the main floor! Upstairs living space, a 5th bdrm w/1/2 bath & 790 SF of unfinished space for you to create what you wish or utilize for ample amounts of storage. 2023 HVAC.
